\par 
\par 
\par There are a few key points that we must consider when devising a system for death on Lu\rquote Tamohr.
\par 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 1.\tab}}\pard \qj \fi-360\li360\ri0\widctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls1\pnrnot0\pndec\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnsp120\pnhang{\pntxta .}}\faauto\ls1\adjustright\rin0\lin360\itap0 {\fs24 Realism

